other.description:
This car park has lifts serving only even-numbered floors. Access to odd-numbered floors is via stairs.
The lifts in this car park are 1970s Cable Lifts.

In this car park, levels CP1-CP3 have red/green lights above each parking space indicating whether the space is vacant or occupied. Level CP4 is an overflow car park & only used at certain times. This car park is accessed by Otis gen2 lifts.
VeloPark parking for buses and disabled badge holders
